11:00 AM  Single Family Aggregation as Interest Rates Rise 


                            Simply as interest rates rise the cost to own homes go up- a net positive for the rental industry. But as interest rates go up it cost more to buy the home- a net negative. But interest rates will not impact all cash buyers-at least right now. This discussion will discuss these points, in depth and find out who the winners and losers will be going forward as interest rates continue their inevitable climb.• Impact on homebuyers • Historical impact on apartment rental market… Does it translate?
                            




