Our Mission

 


By breathing new life into neglected multifamily properties, we plan to generate positive returns for our investors, while improving the quality of life for residents and surrounding communities.
 
At Impact Housing, our top priority is to have happy residents, who stay and pay (and refer their friends), which in turn, results in happy managers and happy investors.  To this end, we measure rate of return two ways—profits and impact. We earn profits from the impact investing in housing has on people’s lives and on resident retention. It’s a true symbiotic relationship.

 




